Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我煮了咖啡  低咖咖啡\N{\fs12}I made coffee. It's half-caf.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  太好了  谢谢\N{\fs12}Oh, great. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你写完英语试卷了吗\N{\fs12}You get that, uh, English paper done?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 写完了  - 哦 很好\N{\fs12}- Uh-huh. - Oh, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天跟你的社会工作者聊了聊\N{\fs12}I talked to your social worker yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,希望我能继续领养你\N{\fs12}about moving this adoption along.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗  - 是啊\N{\fs12}- Really? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这周得跟她见几次面\N{\fs12}We're gonna have to meet with her a couple times this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是我之前跟她谈过了啊  - 我知道\N{\fs12}- But I just talked to her. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 可能  她可能想看看我们相处的怎么样\N{\fs12}I think, uh... I think she just wants to see how... how we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那罗伊呢\N{\fs12}What about Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我会找他谈的\N{\fs12}I'll talk to Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  伯顿\N{\fs12}Thanks, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别客气\N{\fs12}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜拜  - 好的  晚点见\N{\fs12}- See you. - Okay. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来了  进来吧  很抱歉\N{\fs12}Here you go. Come on in. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有点小意外\N{\fs12}A little surprise going here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,把东西都拿到楼上吧\N{\fs12}Everything goes upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  直接上去就行\N{\fs12}How are you? Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  不把它拿走的话其它东西放不进去\N{\fs12}Sir, we can't fit this in until that's out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  让我  先把抽屉清空一下\N{\fs12}Oh, let me... empty these drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.14,0:01:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会容易拿一点\N{\fs12}It'll be a little easier to move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去几楼  - 呃 去法律服务部\N{\fs12}- What floor? - Uh, Legal Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我就去那\N{\fs12}Ah, that's where I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗\N{\fs12}You need some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不用了  我自己可以解决  没问题\N{\fs12}No, no. I got it. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮点忙吗\N{\fs12}A little help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都听我说\N{\fs12}Everybody listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我这有五千份竞选传单\N{\fs12}I got five thousand campaign flyers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,请大家都拿一些  分发出去\N{\fs12}Please, everybody... take some and disseminate them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,走到哪  发到哪\N{\fs12}anywhere and everywhere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,艾米莉·伯恩斯利来找路易莎·阿彻\N{\fs12}Emily Bernsley for Louisa Archer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都加把劲  还有两周就到选举日了\N{\fs12}Come on, people! Only two weeks till Election Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  劳瑞\N{\fs12}Hey, Laurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,市议会的吗\N{\fs12}City Council?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我是一个独立运营者\N{\fs12}Yeah. I'm running as an Independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,给我拿几张吧\N{\fs12}I'll take a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,劳瑞  菲利普最近怎么样\N{\fs12}Laurie, what's going on with Philip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利普的养母不想要他\N{\fs12}Phillip's foster mother doesn't want him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为是奥罗克一家收养了他\N{\fs12}I thought the O'Rourkes were adopting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们刚刚有一个小女儿  - 是的\N{\fs12}- They just had a baby girl. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这个孩子上周受伤了  头上缝了八针\N{\fs12}The baby was injured last month. She had eight stitches in her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fs12}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,婴儿座椅从阳台上掉下来了  孩子那时候正坐在里面\N{\fs12}The infant seat fell off the counter. The baby was in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们怪菲利普吗  - 那时候并没有\N{\fs12}- They blame Philip? - Not then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是昨天奥罗克太太说菲利普在吓唬小宝宝\N{\fs12}But yesterday Mrs. O'Rourke claimed that Philip was threatening the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么吓的  - 没说\N{\fs12}- How? - Didn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她就打电话过来让我们把他接走\N{\fs12}She just called and told us to pick him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 艾米丽吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- Emily? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是路易莎·阿切尔·露露\N{\fs12}I'm Louisa Archer. Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 你好\N{\fs12}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你是伯恩斯利法官的女儿  对吧\N{\fs12}You're Judge Bernsley's daughter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你能来志愿服务真的是太好了\N{\fs12}It's really nice of you to volunteer like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我在法学院曾选修过关于儿童权益的课程\N{\fs12}I took a course on children's rights in law school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了\N{\fs12}Well, this looks great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  那你什么时候可以正式开始呢\N{\fs12}Uh... when can you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚结束一个案子  所以现在就有时间\N{\fs12}I just finished a case, so I'm free right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  好的\N{\fs12}Oh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,露露  你拿传单了吗\N{\fs12}Lulu? Did you get any flyers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么  - 我的竞选传单\N{\fs12}- What? - My campaign flyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话  多拿点  帮我发一发\N{\fs12}lf you could, take a bunch and spread 'em around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 又见面了 - 嗨\N{\fs12}- Hello again. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,桑德拉  别急着走\N{\fs12}Sandra? Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,拿点传单\N{\fs12}Take some flyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利普  你有吓唬那个小孩吗\N{\fs12}Philip, did you threaten the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  我没有对孩子做任何事情\N{\fs12}I didn't do anything to the baby, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们打算怎么处置我\N{\fs12}What's gonna happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  你知道的  劳瑞会尽量给你找一个新家\N{\fs12}Uh... you know, um, Laurie will try to find you a new fam--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能待在奥罗克家了吗\N{\fs12}I can't stay with the O'Rourkes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不能了\N{\fs12}Not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是去看了看宝宝\N{\fs12}I just looked at the baby
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,之后想亲一下她\N{\fs12}and went to give her a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮就开始冲我大喊  让我滚开\N{\fs12}Annie starts yelling at me and telling me to keep away
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,说我会伤到宝宝\N{\fs12}and that I was gonna hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我没想伤害她\N{\fs12}I wasn't gonna hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得玩具都在哪吗\N{\fs12}You remember where the toys are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可以先出去玩一会吗\N{\fs12}You mind just going out and playing for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,让我和劳瑞聊一会\N{\fs12}While Laurie and I talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,别客气\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  呃  当那个孩子受伤的时候\N{\fs12}So, uh, when the baby was injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,奥罗克太太有说看见他把孩子推下阳台吗\N{\fs12}did Mrs. O'Rourke say that she saw him push her off the counter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有  他那时在她转身看不见的地方\N{\fs12}No. He was in the area, she turned around,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 之后她就看见  - 好吧\N{\fs12}- the next thing she knew... - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我所知道的就是奥罗克一家不想再收养菲利普了\N{\fs12}All I know is the O'Rourkes don't want Philip anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,快上车\N{\fs12}Come on. Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  怎么了\N{\fs12}Burton. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你问什么不告诉我这些事\N{\fs12}Why didn't you tell me about these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你不让我参加青少年匹兹堡小姐的选拔\N{\fs12}You didn't let me try out for Miss Teen Pittsburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我想让你专注于你的学业\N{\fs12}Because I wanted you to focus on your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以获胜的\N{\fs12}I could've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝  成为青少年匹兹堡小姐并能帮助你通过数学考试\N{\fs12}Honey, being Miss Teen Pittsburgh is not gonna help you pass math.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我两个都能做好的  模特和学业\N{\fs12}I can do both. Modeling and school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,至少现在  我希望你能专心学习\N{\fs12}For right now, I want you to focus on your school work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我打算跟这个摄影师聊聊\N{\fs12}And I want to talk to that photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么  - 因为我是你的监护人\N{\fs12}- Why? - Because I'm your guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我需要知道关于你的一切\N{\fs12}Because I have to know everything you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一切\N{\fs12}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  他叫什么名字\N{\fs12}Now what's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,马尔科姆·里维斯\N{\fs12}Malcolm Reeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他的影棚在哪里\N{\fs12}Where's his studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在北区  爱丽丝大街\N{\fs12}On the North Side. Alice Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,马尔科姆跟许多模特和演员一起工作\N{\fs12}Malcolm works with lots of models and actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至为百货公司做陈列\N{\fs12}And he even does layouts for department stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  就好好做你的作业可以吗  我一会就回来\N{\fs12}Honey, just do your homework, all right? I'll be back in a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿\N{\fs12}Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,宝宝有绞痛\N{\fs12}The baby has colic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我一晚上大概睡了两个小时\N{\fs12}I get... I get, like, two hours of sleep a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她就是  一直一直哭\N{\fs12}And, uh, she just cries and cries and cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以之后  法林先生  你知道的  我并不是超人\N{\fs12}And then, you know, l... I am not superhuman, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗  我不能一边照顾希瑟  一边成为菲利普的好妈妈\N{\fs12}Okay? I can't look after Heather and be a good mom to Philip as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能这样  这对他也不公平  对我  对我也不公平\N{\fs12}I can't do that. It's not fair to him. It's... it's not fair to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,之后菲利普就做了这样的事情\N{\fs12}And then Philip does something like that.
