Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,香农过来跟我说  她说你不让他参加选美\N{\fs12}Shannon comes to me, and she says you won't let her do some pageants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,她说你一直逼着她学一些她不擅长的课程\N{\fs12}She says you keep making her take classes she's not good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她总觉得自己什么都做不好\N{\fs12}Says she feels stupid all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  她想成为一个模特  我不会成为扼杀她梦想的人\N{\fs12}So she's got a dream to model. I'm not gonna be the guy who kills it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊  我觉得我们应该再谈一谈\N{\fs12}Roy, I think you and l better have another little talk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,关于收养的问题  好吗\N{\fs12}about finalizing this adoption, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  嘿  我有工作了  我在镇子安定下来了\N{\fs12}Well, hey, I got a job. I've been here in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我一周看香农一次  我在做我应该做的事情\N{\fs12}I see Shannon once a week. I'm doing what I'm supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是她的爸爸  不是你\N{\fs12}I'm her dad, man, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你在影响我  你知道吗\N{\fs12}You're screwing me, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是香农想要的\N{\fs12}This is what Shannon wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这并不是她跟我说的\N{\fs12}Well, that's not what she says to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  这是她跟社会服务部说的\N{\fs12}Well, that's what she told Social Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,记录上都有的\N{\fs12}That's on the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你再逼着她的话  她会在法庭上再说出来的\N{\fs12}She'll say it again in a court of law if you make her do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你就同意收养就可以了\N{\fs12}Just agree to the adoption.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你会有探视权\N{\fs12}I'll give you visitation rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一万\N{\fs12}Ten thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一万美金  你想怎么样就怎么样\N{\fs12}Ten thousand... I'll agree to whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  罗伊\N{\fs12}Oh, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  劳瑞\N{\fs12}Hey, Laurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 伯顿  很高兴见到你  - 最近怎么样\N{\fs12}- Burton. Nice to see you. - How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还不错  谢谢  - 进来吧\N{\fs12}- Fine, thanks. - Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fs12}Have a seat there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 最近怎么样啊  - 还好  你呢\N{\fs12}- How've you been? - Okay. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还可以  谢谢\N{\fs12}Good. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那\N{\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我今早开了一个会\N{\fs12}You know I had a meeting this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,和瑟蒙德学院的校长\N{\fs12}with the Headmistress at the Thurmond Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,海登太太  是的  她是一个  一个很了不起的女士\N{\fs12}Mrs. Hayden, yeah. She's a... she's a terrific lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能了解香农在学校都在做什么\N{\fs12}I assume you know how Shannon's been doing in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  是的 是的  我们在努力学习了\N{\fs12}Oh, yeah, yeah. Yeah, we're working on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃  给她请了一个家教  而且我也每天给她检查作业\N{\fs12}l, uh, hired a tutor and I check her homework every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  我觉得  她也在进步\N{\fs12}and I think, uh... I think she's improving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,海登太太并不认为香农拥有在瑟蒙德取得成功才能\N{\fs12}Mrs. Hayden doesn't think Shannon has the skills she needs to succeed at Thurmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  这也是我们一直努力的原因\N{\fs12}Uh... that's what we're working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她说她应该在五年级  不是八年级\N{\fs12}She says she should be in the fifth grade, not the eighth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  这太荒谬了\N{\fs12}Oh, that's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  他们已经建议香农转校了\N{\fs12}Burton, they're recommending that Shannon be placed in another school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,专区一个能满足她特殊需求的学校\N{\fs12}a school that can meet her special needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,特殊需求\N{\fs12}Special needs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她只是  她只是还没有准备好去你们让她去的学校\N{\fs12}It's just that she's... not prepared for the school you've placed her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,只是这样  伯顿\N{\fs12}That's all, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  伯顿\N{\fs12}Hi, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  亲爱的\N{\fs12}Hi, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊就是过来打个招呼\N{\fs12}Roy just came over to say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  好的  去车里等我可以吗\N{\fs12}Yeah. Right. Go wait in the car, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去吧  去吧  - 拜拜\N{\fs12}- Go ahead. Go on. - I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,拜\N{\fs12}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我想跟你说的\N{\fs12}This is exactly what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能来看我自己的女儿吗\N{\fs12}I'm not allowed to see my own daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没我的允许就不行\N{\fs12}Not without my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是跟她说清楚整件事\N{\fs12}I was just talking to her about this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看看她想怎样\N{\fs12}Seeing what she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  法林先生\N{\fs12}I mean, Mr. Fallin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  你是对的\N{\fs12}Hey, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她想跟你在一起\N{\fs12}She wants to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我今天跟劳瑞·索尔特和海登太太谈过了\N{\fs12}Listen, I talked to Laurie Solt and Mrs. Hayden today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:18:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  呃  我们觉得瑟蒙德也许并不是一个适合你的学校\N{\fs12}and, uh, we're thinking maybe Thurmond is not exactly the right school for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那我能回到我之前的学校吗\N{\fs12}I can go back to my old school, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不行  我们正在想着去新边界\N{\fs12}No, no. We're thinking about New Borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么  - 新边界\N{\fs12}- What? - New Borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一所弱智学校\N{\fs12}That's a school for retards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不  并不是   事实上  这是一个还不错的学校\N{\fs12}No it's not. Actually, it's a pretty good school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一个弱智学校\N{\fs12}It's a school for retards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝  我  我知道今年对于你来说是非常艰难的一年\N{\fs12}Honey... l, uh... I know this has been a tough year for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的改变和周围的一切\N{\fs12}all the changes and everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  要不你就去试一两个学期\N{\fs12}but... why don't you just try this for a semester or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我们再定下一步该做什么\N{\fs12}Then we'll figure out what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,把我送回原来的学校吧  我不会去那的\N{\fs12}Just send me back to my old school, then. I'm not going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我之后再跟你说  晚点我们再聊这件事\N{\fs12}All right, I'll tell you what. Let's talk about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们该吃个晚餐再看一个电影\N{\fs12}Maybe we'll have dinner and go to a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗\N{\fs12}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fs12}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,能进来吗\N{\fs12}You mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  没事  进来吧\N{\fs12}Oh... no, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是需要打几个电话\N{\fs12}Just have to make some calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  帮我找一下安德鲁·莱文森\N{\fs12}Hello, Andrew Levinson, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁  我是艾米丽·伯恩斯利\N{\fs12}Andrew. Emily Bernsley.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我打电话来想跟你说一下你的软禁试点计划\N{\fs12}I'm calling about your house arrest pilot program.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我这有一个孩子很适合\N{\fs12}I'm representing a kid who would be perfect for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我要去其他地方工作\N{\fs12}No. I'll go work somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯\N{\fs12}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我还需要一千美金  艾比 需要重新印传单\N{\fs12}I just need another thousand dollars, Abby, to reprint the flyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  我很认真  艾比  我不想成为一谈笑话\N{\fs12}No, no, I'm serious, Abby. I don't want to be the butt of a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,赫伯·奥罗克刚刚打电话来了  他妻子同意接回菲利普了\N{\fs12}Herb O'Rourke just called. His wife agreed to take Philip back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是  好消息\N{\fs12}So... nice news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是  是啊  真是个好消息\N{\fs12}Yeah. Yeah. That's good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息\N{\fs12}Nice news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我再努力一点  我能通过瑟蒙德的考试的\N{\fs12}I can pass my classes at Thurmond... if I try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想  我会再努力一点的  伯顿\N{\fs12}I guess... I'll have to try harder, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也许  亲爱的你需要一些基础的技巧\N{\fs12}Well, maybe you need some basic skills, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  呃  并不是你的问题  但是如果你\N{\fs12}I mean... uh... It's not your fault, but if you... if you had...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果你有一些基础的  - 我能做到的  伯顿\N{\fs12}- if you had the basics... - I can do it, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,格里森太太  我的数学老师  说我可以参加明天的补偿考试\N{\fs12}Mrs. Gleason, my math teacher, said I could take a make-up test tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我之前学过一点\N{\fs12}And I've studied a little bit for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,明天吗\N{\fs12}Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备好了\N{\fs12}I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做到的\N{\fs12}I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什么考试\N{\fs12}Test on what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,分数和百分数  类似于这种的\N{\fs12}Fractions and percents. Stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  是么\N{\fs12}Oh. Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,给我一个百分数  然后我把它转换成分数\N{\fs12}Give me a percentage, and I can turn it into a fraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\fs12}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把它转换成分数吗\N{\fs12}Can you turn this into a fraction?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,算了  宝贝  你现在不需要做这些的\N{\fs12}Well... you don't have to do this now, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我可以的  伯顿  我不是笨蛋\N{\fs12}Uh, I can do it, Burton. I'm not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我当然知道你不是笨蛋  我知道的  亲爱的\N{\fs12}Oh, I know you're not stupid, honey. I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧  咱们回家吧\N{\fs12}Come on, let's just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,走啦\N{\fs12}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs12}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,走啦  宝贝\N{\fs12}Come on, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你  你之前说我们要去看电影的\N{\fs12}You-- you said we were going to the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,香农  别无理取闹  现在要我们回去了\N{\fs12}Shannon, this is ridiculous. Now come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过我们要出去的\N{\fs12}You said we were going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:21:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝  下车  然后进屋\N{\fs12}Honey, get out of the car and come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么在这  你在我家做什么\N{\fs12}What are you doing here? What are you doing in my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 怎么了\N{\fs12}- Hey. - What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊和  一些其他人\N{\fs12}Roy and... some other guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看见他的脸\N{\fs12}I didn't get a look at his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要偷你妈妈的珠宝\N{\fs12}trying to steal your mother's jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.35,0:23:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我追他们\N{\fs12}I ran after 'em...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是   他们把我推倒了\N{\fs12}but... shoved me down...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,撞到了头\N{\fs12}hit my damn head.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在感觉怎么样\N{\fs12}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  有点晕  没什么大问题\N{\fs12}Oh, dizzy. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你  我需要你今晚照顾一下香农\N{\fs12}Look... I need you... I need you to take care of Shannon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  爸爸  我\N{\fs12}Oh, Dad... l...
