Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  香农  告诉我\N{\fs12}Hey, Shannon, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.58,0:23:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊是怎么知道珠宝的事的\N{\fs12}How did Roy know about the jewelry?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.13,0:23:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉他的  是吗\N{\fs12}You told him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.73,0:24:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是你告诉他的\N{\fs12}You told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.61,0:24:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊  借了一大笔钱\N{\fs12}Roy... borrowed a lot of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给我买化妆品\N{\fs12}to buy all this makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.77,0:24:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这堆化妆品\N{\fs12}This shipment of makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.44,0:24:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他没有检查看看颜色奇不奇怪\N{\fs12}And he didn't check to see it was all strange colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他以为就是正常的颜色  但是其实是一堆卖不掉的奇怪颜色\N{\fs12}He thought it was normal, but it was all funny colors, so he couldn't sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.26,0:24:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好明早七点走\N{\fs12}Be ready to leave at seven in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.58,0:24:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,发生的一切我很抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.79,0:24:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一放学就回我家\N{\fs12}Just be back at my house right after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.05,0:25:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  我没有想过会发生这样的事\N{\fs12}Nick, I didn't want any of this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.69,0:25:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你会告诉伯顿的  是吗\N{\fs12}You're gonna tell Burton, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.35,0:25:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的这些   你会告诉他吗\N{\fs12}What I said, you're gonna tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.79,0:25:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一放学就回去我家\N{\fs12}Just be back at my house right after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.10,0:25:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.93,0:25:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.56,0:25:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样了\N{\fs12}How're you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.11,0:25:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  还那样吧\N{\fs12}Oh, about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.96,0:25:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛  那还好吧\N{\fs12}Yeah. Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.62,0:25:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是香农告诉罗伊珠宝的事情的\N{\fs12}Shannon told Roy about the jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.44,0:25:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她给他留了门\N{\fs12}She left the door open for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.63,0:25:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼古拉斯  - 哦  爸爸\N{\fs12}- Nicholas... - Oh, Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.74,0:25:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她会一直使你陷到这样的麻烦中\N{\fs12}she's gonna keep dragging you into this kinda trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.43,0:25:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她还是个孩子\N{\fs12}She's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.68,0:26:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她是一个帮助她爸爸闯入你家的孩子\N{\fs12}She's a kid that helped her father break into your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.01,0:26:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她就只是一个孩子啊\N{\fs12}She's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.51,0:26:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么情况\N{\fs12}What is this about... really?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.89,0:26:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  你为什么一定要有这样一个人在你的生活中呢\N{\fs12}I mean... why do you need someone like this in your life right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.74,0:26:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我得走了\N{\fs12}Uh... I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.21,0:26:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.57,0:26:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要我来接你的时候  就直接  给我打电话\N{\fs12}Just... just call me when you... when you need me to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.47,0:26:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿\N{\fs12}Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.09,0:26:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿\N{\fs12}Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.12,0:27:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒  伯顿\N{\fs12}Hi, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.97,0:27:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  伯顿\N{\fs12}Hi, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.65,0:27:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.53,0:27:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在应该在学校\N{\fs12}You should be in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.92,0:27:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  我就是\N{\fs12}I know, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.15,0:27:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎么不在学校\N{\fs12}Why aren't you in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.13,0:27:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克告诉你我做的事了吗\N{\fs12}Nick told you what I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.66,0:27:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉了\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.53,0:27:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  伯顿\N{\fs12}I'm so sorry, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.29,0:27:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要做这样的事情\N{\fs12}Why in the world would you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.22,0:27:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊说他很需要钱\N{\fs12}Roy said he needed money.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.85,0:27:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道当你做这些事情的时候  会给你带来很多麻烦吗\N{\fs12}Don't you know when you do things like that, you get in a lot of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.91,0:27:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.18,0:28:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你很生气\N{\fs12}I'm angry with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.68,0:28:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,非常生气\N{\fs12}Very angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.02,0:28:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.56,0:28:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  去外边等着  好吗\N{\fs12}Listen, wait outside, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.75,0:28:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一小会就好\N{\fs12}It'll be just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.76,0:28:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心  亲爱的  我们很快就好\N{\fs12}Don't worry, hon. We'll be right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.36,0:28:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.38,0:28:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生因右侧颞区头部受伤而来我们医院\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin comes to us with a closed-head injury to the right temporal region.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.99,0:28:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,软组织肿胀  但是没有颅内出血\N{\fs12}He experienced soft-tissue swelling but no evidence of intracranial hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.70,0:28:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  而且  通过CT扫描也没有发现任何颅骨骨折\N{\fs12}Uh... and, uh, no skull fracture also noted on the CT Scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.81,0:28:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  马斯特先生\N{\fs12}Ah, Mr. Master-sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.93,0:28:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真好笑\N{\fs12}Now that's... that's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.43,0:28:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我得告诉你\N{\fs12}But I'll tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.58,0:28:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天出去把那些传单撕下来\N{\fs12}I went out today to pull those flyers down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.51,0:28:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不论到哪  我都停下来跟那的人聊天\N{\fs12}Everywhere I went, I stopped to talk to people--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.36,0:28:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,关于我的竞选和我的想法\N{\fs12}about my campaign, about my ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.64,0:28:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你知道吗  人们都在认真听\N{\fs12}And you know what? People were listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.69,0:28:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉  这次错误的印刷已经吸引了他们的注意\N{\fs12}I mean, this whole misprint got their attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.42,0:29:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他们  他们是真的在听我说\N{\fs12}and they... they actually listened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.95,0:29:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你继续加油吧  - 我会的\N{\fs12}- Good for you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.30,0:29:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然会的\N{\fs12}I mean... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.68,0:29:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.01,0:29:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  尼克  你已经不在布尔西科的案子了\N{\fs12}Oh, Nick, you're off the Bulseco case.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.97,0:29:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我吗  - 艾米丽解决了\N{\fs12}- I am? - Emily resolved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.22,0:29:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哦  是她解决的吗  - 是啊  真是不可思议\N{\fs12}- Oh, she did? - Yeah, she's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.79,0:29:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是不可思议\N{\fs12}Really incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.13,0:29:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fs12}Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.35,0:29:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  你还在啊\N{\fs12}Oh, you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.70,0:29:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,露露给了我一些你的案子\N{\fs12}Lulu gave me a couple of your cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.27,0:29:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很好啊  - 所以我有一些工作需要做\N{\fs12}- Great. - So I have to do some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.69,0:29:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.00,0:29:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我就只是工作  而且你也可以\N{\fs12}I'll just work... and you can, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.55,0:29:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  尼克\N{\fs12}Excuse me, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.14,0:29:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉打扰到你们\N{\fs12}Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.66,0:29:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,奥罗克太太有产后抑郁症\N{\fs12}Mrs. O'Rourke has post-partum depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.57,0:30:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她\N{\fs12}She...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.46,0:30:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上她状态不太好\N{\fs12}This morning she had kind of a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.02,0:30:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她要伤害菲利普  但是他光着脚跑出来了\N{\fs12}She tried to hit Philip, and he ran outside in his bare feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.20,0:30:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她把门锁上了\N{\fs12}She locked the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.18,0:30:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,直到她的丈夫下班回来才让他进屋\N{\fs12}Didn't let him back in till her husband came home from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.48,0:30:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我就只是在房间里写作业\N{\fs12}I was just doing my homework in the family room.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.30,0:30:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她就开始冲我大喊\N{\fs12}And she starts screaming at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.03,0:30:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利普的脸上  手上  还有脚上都刚接受完冻伤治疗\N{\fs12}Philip was treated for frostbite on his face, his hands, and his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.47,0:30:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,奥罗克夫人现在在哪呢\N{\fs12}Where's Mrs. O'Rourke now?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.13,0:30:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们把她送去医院了\N{\fs12}They took her to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.48,0:30:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚说她怎么了  她得了什么病\N{\fs12}What did you say about her? What does she have?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.65,0:30:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  她生了这样一种病\N{\fs12}She's got this thing, honey,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.70,0:30:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就是有的人怀宝宝的时候会得的病\N{\fs12}that people sometimes get when they have a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.74,0:30:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这种病会使他们行为很奇怪\N{\fs12}It makes them act funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.57,0:30:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是她的错  只是她现在生了这样的一种病\N{\fs12}It's not her fault. She's just kinda sick right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.61,0:30:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那我能回家了吗\N{\fs12}Do I get to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.58,0:30:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝  我们会给你另外找一个好地方的\N{\fs12}We'll find a good place for you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.75,0:30:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.07,0:30:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会给你找一个更好的地方的\N{\fs12}We'll find a better place for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.42,0:31:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白  但是如果你有其他的消息\N{\fs12}I understand, but if you learn anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.67,0:31:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能告诉我\N{\fs12}would you... would you let me know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.60,0:31:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感激  谢谢\N{\fs12}I appreciate it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.99,0:31:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好点了吗\N{\fs12}Feeling any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.18,0:31:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近有香农的消息吗\N{\fs12}Have you heard anything from Shannon recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.87,0:31:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  我早上把她放在学校了\N{\fs12}No. I dropped her at school this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.33,0:31:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚在这待了一会  之后就走了\N{\fs12}She was here a while ago. She just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.27,0:31:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才就是学校的电话\N{\fs12}That was the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.56,0:31:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说她今天根本没去上学\N{\fs12}They said she never showed up at all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.38,0:31:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.60,0:31:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,说你早上打电话过去了\N{\fs12}Said you called this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.20,0:31:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而且跟他们说她今天不舒服\N{\fs12}and told them that she was not feeling well...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.38,0:31:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊  根本没有  我没打电话  我没给学校打电话\N{\fs12}No, that's not true. I didn't call. I didn't call the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.02,0:31:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  别担心  她可能跟罗伊在一起呢\N{\fs12}Dad, don't worry. She's probably with Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.14,0:31:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能就是\N{\fs12}She's probably just...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.19,0:31:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么\N{\fs12}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.15,0:31:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  你好  我是伯顿·法林\N{\fs12}Uh, yeah, this is Burton·Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.20,0:31:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我的养女香农  是彭妮的朋友\N{\fs12}My foster child Shannon is a... a friend of Penny's.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.75,0:31:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的   是的\N{\fs12}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.87,0:31:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想了解一下  她今天有没有跟香农联系过\N{\fs12}Wondering if, uh... if she had talked to, uh, Shannon at all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.41,0:32:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  不  我在这边等着  谢谢\N{\fs12}No. No, no. I'll-- I'll hold. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.20,0:32:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想的话  我可以开车转一转  找找她\N{\fs12}I can just take a drive around and look for her, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.18,0:32:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哪啊\N{\fs12}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.27,0:32:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 什么\N{\fs12}- Well... - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.15,0:32:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,从昨天开始就没有啊\N{\fs12}Not since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.72,0:32:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没  没有  她不是\N{\fs12}No, no. She wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.32,0:32:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她今天没有去学校  所以\N{\fs12}she wasn't at school today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.54,0:32:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  那好吧  谢谢\N{\fs12}Okay. Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.15,0:32:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  如果你有她的任何消息  可不可以给我回个电话\N{\fs12}Uh... would you... would you give me a call if you hear anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.32,0:32:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.26,0:32:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她经常去哪逛\N{\fs12}Where does she hang out?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.77,0:32:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  商场  我真不知道\N{\fs12}I don't know. The mall... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.17,0:32:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我可以开着车然后\N{\fs12}Well, I can just jump in the car and...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.41,0:32:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.11,0:32:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.16,0:32:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.91,0:32:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  不  不  不  我马上就到\N{\fs12}Oh, no, no, no. I'll be right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.08,0:32:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.94,0:32:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,警察找到罗伊了\N{\fs12}The police found Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.15,0:32:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他有香农的消息\N{\fs12}He says he has some information about Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.86,0:32:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.29,0:33:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊想做一个交易\N{\fs12}Roy wants to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.76,0:33:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮他找到他的亲身女儿吗\N{\fs12}To help find his own daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.20,0:33:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他想做个交易\N{\fs12}He wants to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.52,0:33:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他会请求减刑吗  - 是的\N{\fs12}- He will plea down to a misdemeanor? - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.37,0:33:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,地方检察官会同意吗\N{\fs12}And the DA's gonna go for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.69,0:33:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我同意的话  毕竟我是受害者  所以\N{\fs12}lf I approve. I'm the victim, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.32,0:33:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你别同意\N{\fs12}You're not doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.41,0:33:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他会帮我找到香农\N{\fs12}He can help me find Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.91,0:33:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能就这样放过这个混蛋\N{\fs12}You can't just let this guy off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.42,0:33:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  他说他有消息\N{\fs12}Nicholas, he says he has information.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.37,0:33:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,香农离家出走是因为她对你做的事\N{\fs12}Shannon ran away because of what she did to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.13,0:33:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,先想想这个吧\N{\fs12}Now think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.48,0:33:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是丢了  爸爸  她只是离家出走\N{\fs12}She's not missing, Dad. She ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.95,0:33:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,当她想再跟你要什么的时候  她自然就会回来\N{\fs12}She will be back the moment she wants something more from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.87,0:33:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  尼克  如果你不想帮忙  那就别在这捣乱  好吗\N{\fs12}Listen, Nick, if you don't want to help, I don't want you here. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.38,0:33:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  回家去吧\N{\fs12}All right. Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.90,0:33:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.37,0:33:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她和马尔科姆在一起\N{\fs12}She's with Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.84,0:33:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 马尔科姆  - 那个摄影师吗\N{\fs12}- Malcolm? - The photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.50,0:33:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么知道的  - 香农给我打电话了\N{\fs12}- How do you know that? - Shannon called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.90,0:33:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她说她现在有困难\N{\fs12}She says she was in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.18,0:33:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她  呃  她说你不想要她了\N{\fs12}She, uh... she said you didn't want her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.19,0:33:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有说过这样的话\N{\fs12}I never said anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.02,0:33:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去找她  但是我还没到马尔科姆家  他们就把我抓起来了\N{\fs12}I tried to find her, but they picked me up before I could get to Malcolm's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.27,0:34:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.15,0:34:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.62,0:34:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她不在这\N{\fs12}She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.23,0:34:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs12}Well, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.75,0:34:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在里面找到了些别的东西  一些女人的照片\N{\fs12}We found some things inside... pictures of women.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.67,0:34:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大多数都是成人的东西\N{\fs12}Most of it's just your garden variety adult stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.26,0:34:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们也的确找到了让我们不安的东西  小孩子的照片\N{\fs12}But we did find some photos that disturbed us-- young kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.36,0:34:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  天哪\N{\fs12}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.47,0:34:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有香农的吗\N{\fs12}Any of those Shannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.41,0:34:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没有\N{\fs12}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.72,0:34:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,先回家吧\N{\fs12}Just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.73,0:34:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有其他消息我们会再通知你\N{\fs12}We'll call you if we hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.90,0:34:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.93,0:34:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有其他消息你们会通知我吗\N{\fs12}You'll... you'll call me if you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.36,0:34:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会的\N{\fs12}We'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.05,0:35:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.33,0:35:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,警察搜查马尔科姆的摄影棚\N{\fs12}The police went through Malcolm's studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.37,0:35:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了很多小女孩的照片\N{\fs12}Found a lot of pictures of young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.28,0:35:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,儿童色情照片  罗伊\N{\fs12}Child pornography, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.71,0:35:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能把她单独扔给这样一个\N{\fs12}How could you leave her alone with that kind of--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.37,0:35:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我会料想到事情会发生成这样吗\N{\fs12}You think I had any idea that was going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.84,0:35:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你介绍的他们\N{\fs12}You introduced them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.90,0:35:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是那个让她觉得自己是一个垃圾的人\N{\fs12}I wasn't the one who made her feel like a piece of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.72,0:35:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在只需要让我知道关于马尔科姆的一切\N{\fs12}You just have to let me know everything you know about Malcolm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.91,0:35:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之前一起做生意\N{\fs12}We were in business together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.60,0:35:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟我提到了这些化妆品\N{\fs12}He told me about this shipment of makeup,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.37,0:35:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们从一些人哪里借了钱\N{\fs12}so we borrowed some money from some guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.00,0:35:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我们又还不起\N{\fs12}and we can't pay them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.60,0:35:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你闯进我家的原因吗\N{\fs12}That's why you broke in my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.98,0:35:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要钱\N{\fs12}I needed the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.61,0:35:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为他们在一起安全吗\N{\fs12}Do you think she's safe with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.08,0:35:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,马尔科姆不会伤害她的\N{\fs12}Malcolm's not gonna hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.81,0:35:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的\N{\fs12}How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.03,0:35:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他有点喜欢她\N{\fs12}'Cause he kinda likes her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.53,0:35:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.54,0:35:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,马尔科姆喜欢她  法林先生\N{\fs12}Malcolm likes her, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.88,0:35:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她才十三岁\N{\fs12}She's thirteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.70,0:35:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也许在你的世界里  13岁还是一个孩子\N{\fs12}Maybe in your world, thirteen's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.97,0:36:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在我们的世界  我的意思是  香农的妈妈15岁时我们认识了\N{\fs12}ln ours... I mean, Shannon's mom was fifteen when I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.82,0:36:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她16岁的时候我们有了香农\N{\fs12}She was sixteen when she had Shannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.81,0:36:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  马尔科姆需要钱  然后  卖儿童色情片\N{\fs12}So... Malcolm needs money and... sells child pornography,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.80,0:36:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他跟香农单独在一起  是吧\N{\fs12}and he's alone with Shannon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.57,0:36:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不关心你来自于哪个世界  罗伊\N{\fs12}I don't care what world you're from, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.58,0:36:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,实在太糟糕了\N{\fs12}This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.52,0:36:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你想要收养菲利普\N{\fs12}You say you want Philip in your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.38,0:36:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是希望能再有一次机会  法官大人  我们之前不知道\N{\fs12}We just want another chance, Your Honor. We didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.81,0:36:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望能再有一次机会\N{\fs12}I just want another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.16,0:36:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,索尔特女士  你怎么看\N{\fs12}Ms. Solt, what's your position?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.62,0:36:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为已经没有给像菲利普这样的孩子提供的好地方了\N{\fs12}I think there aren't many good placements for a kid like Philip.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.66,0:36:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这并不是最好的建议\N{\fs12}That's not the greatest recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.36,0:36:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是就事论事\N{\fs12}I'm just being realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.12,0:36:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生呢\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.79,0:36:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,奥罗克太太  呃  指责菲利普伤害他们的孩子\N{\fs12}Mrs. O'Rourke, uh, accused Philip of abusing their baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.73,0:36:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她虐待菲利普\N{\fs12}then she abused Philip.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.33,0:36:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们带着孩子出院之前\N{\fs12}Before we left the hospital with the baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.41,0:36:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一个护士过来跟我们提到了产后抑郁症\N{\fs12}a nurse came to talk to us, and she mentioned post-partum depression,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.51,0:36:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在所有的事情中\N{\fs12}but amongst a whole list of other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.46,0:36:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我第一次听说它  那我们之前又怎么会知道\N{\fs12}That was the first time I'd ever heard of it before, so how were we to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.13,0:37:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,奥罗克先生  你的太太什么时候出院\N{\fs12}Mr. O'Rourke, when is your wife due to be released?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.66,0:37:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,两周之后\N{\fs12}ln two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.88,0:37:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这有一封她医生的解释说明书\N{\fs12}Got a letter here from her doctor explaining everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.25,0:37:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想给她正确的药物治疗  就这样\N{\fs12}I just want to get her medications right, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.66,0:37:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果菲利普想回到奥罗克家  那他就可以\N{\fs12}lf Philip wishes to return to the O'Rourkes, he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.79,0:37:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是由菲利普决定\N{\fs12}But it's up to Philip.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.85,0:37:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,复印这一页  之后还有这一页\N{\fs12}Photocopy this page and then just this page,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.09,0:37:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,弄好之后  麻烦拿到我的办公室\N{\fs12}and when you're done, if you could bring it to my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.88,0:37:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼克  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- Nick. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.42,0:37:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能跟你聊一会吗  - 当然可以\N{\fs12}- Can I talk to you for a sec? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.73,0:37:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是关于艾米丽的\N{\fs12}It's about Emily Bernsley.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.85,0:37:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃  今天给威廉·柯克打电话了\N{\fs12}l, uh... called William·Kirk today,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.90,0:37:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就是跟她说她工作表现很好\N{\fs12}just to say what a great job she was doing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.88,0:37:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也是为拖了她这么久道歉\N{\fs12}and to apologize for keeping her so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.06,0:37:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他说他上周解雇了她\N{\fs12}and he said that he fired her last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.95,0:37:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真的么  为什么啊\N{\fs12}Really? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.22,0:37:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他没说\N{\fs12}He didn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.25,0:37:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他说因为她的爸爸  事情很尴尬\N{\fs12}He said it was awkward because of her dad and...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.55,0:37:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  我认为她是一个很好的律师\N{\fs12}Anyway, I think that she's a really good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.22,0:37:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该跟她说什么\N{\fs12}I just don't know what I should say to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.68,0:37:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你爸爸打电话了  -是吗\N{\fs12}- Your dad called. - He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.36,0:37:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,说他在家\N{\fs12}Said he's at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.60,0:38:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢在这吗\N{\fs12}Do you like it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.20,0:38:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.72,0:38:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.10,0:38:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 菲利普来了  - 好的\N{\fs12}- Philip's here. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.30,0:38:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,最近怎样\N{\fs12}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.76,0:38:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还好\N{\fs12}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.60,0:38:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你呢  - 还好  还不错\N{\fs12}- You? - Yeah, fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.25,0:38:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 好的\N{\fs12}- Okay.- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.44,0:38:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.63,0:38:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.91,0:38:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利普\N{\fs12}Philip.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.83,0:38:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那  我们跟法官说过了  他说你自己决定\N{\fs12}So we, uh, we spoke to the judge, and he said it's... it's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.27,0:38:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想回去  那就回去\N{\fs12}lf you want to go back home, then you can go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.73,0:38:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果你不想  我们就给你找一个更好的\N{\fs12}But if you don't, then we can find you a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.39,0:38:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直说你会给我找一个更好的地方\N{\fs12}You keep saying you'll find me a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.02,0:38:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.14,0:38:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你并不是认真的  是吗\N{\fs12}But you don't really mean it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.72,0:39:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得当时奥罗克一家选择了我\N{\fs12}I remember when the O'Rourkes chose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.02,0:39:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人都不要我\N{\fs12}Nobody else wanted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.72,0:39:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我都记得\N{\fs12}I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.35,0:39:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有其他人想要我  你就会同意\N{\fs12}lf people want somebody like me, you go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.27,0:39:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧  法林先生\N{\fs12}Right, Mr. Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.32,0:39:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧  法林先生\N{\fs12}Right, Mr. Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.64,0:39:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话  我就只想回家\N{\fs12}lf it's okay, I just want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.16,0:39:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,确定吗\N{\fs12}Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.41,0:39:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,确定\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.79,0:39:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拿点吧  发出去啊\N{\fs12}Take some... hand 'em out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.38,0:39:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟艾米丽聊了\N{\fs12}So I spoke to Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.31,0:39:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.39,0:39:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她住在家里  早上跟她爸爸一起上班\N{\fs12}She lives at home, and she commutes in the morning with her dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.70,0:39:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她很担心他怎样接受这个消息\N{\fs12}and she was afraid  how he was gonna take the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.04,0:39:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他不知道她已经被解雇了\N{\fs12}And he doesn't know that she was fired,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.80,0:39:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  这就是她最近一直在这边逛的原因\N{\fs12}so that's why she's been hanging out here all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.01,0:39:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是希望能在这边志愿服务\N{\fs12}I'd still like to volunteer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.28,0:40:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  好啊  当然可以\N{\fs12}Oh, yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.36,0:40:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我是真的喜欢你们在做的事情\N{\fs12}I really like what you guys do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.93,0:40:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.13,0:40:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在得去见我爸爸了\N{\fs12}I have to meet my dad now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.21,0:40:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好  拜拜\N{\fs12}Okay. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.86,0:40:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,拿点吧   给马斯特森投票啊\N{\fs12}Take a few. Vote for Masterson.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.44,0:40:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不给她提供一份工作啊\N{\fs12}Why don't you give her a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.07,0:40:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  也许吧\N{\fs12}Yeah. Yeah. Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.25,0:40:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  之前是你说她不错的\N{\fs12}Well, you said she's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.47,0:40:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.85,0:40:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.70,0:41:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,又跟那个侦探聊了\N{\fs12}Talked to that detective again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.79,0:41:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他们会尽全力的\N{\fs12}He said they'll do the best they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.10,0:41:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.78,0:41:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,尽他们的全力\N{\fs12}The best they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.31,0:41:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的错\N{\fs12}It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.71,0:41:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是我造成的这一切  - 不 爸爸  不怪你\N{\fs12}- I did this. - No, Dad, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.70,0:41:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有错\N{\fs12}You didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.50,0:41:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果明天我还收不到任何消息\N{\fs12}Well... if I don't hear something by tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.10,0:41:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她会回来的  - 哦\N{\fs12}- She'll be back. - Oh.. .
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.99,0:41:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.66,0:41:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是劳瑞·绍尔特\N{\fs12}It's Laurie·Solt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.67,0:41:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.10,0:41:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要进行一个  她明天要跟香农聊关于领养的事\N{\fs12}We had a... She was gonna interview Shannon for the adoption and...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.92,0:42:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 算了  - 不  爸爸\N{\fs12}- Well... - No, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.19,0:42:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我来跟她解释\N{\fs12}I'll talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.22,0:42:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我来解释\N{\fs12}I'll talk to her.
